{"tid":460322,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖） 謝雪心 心姐真係好撚正","createTime":"2017-11-06T14:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T14:21:32.000Z","uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39cb05bc86d5fd479673575a98655f12c9342453","tid":460322,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/220701_b700f77d380c7446de4c5fe4f48d0a2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F220701_b700f77d380c7446de4c5fe4f48d0a2b.jpg&h=93e43b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/220702_c78d4339f8ac0187511f973a5505986e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F220702_c78d4339f8ac0187511f973a5505986e.jpg&h=fff02515&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17f787a03e78169b7f319391901bc43f1b6dedc","tid":460322,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/220701_b700f77d380c7446de4c5fe4f48d0a2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F220701_b700f77d380c7446de4c5fe4f48d0a2b.jpg&h=93e43b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/220702_c78d4339f8ac0187511f973a5505986e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F220702_c78d4339f8ac0187511f973a5505986e.jpg&h=fff02515&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得個頭開得唔錯 我嗰時有幾個角色都覺得有做反角嘅可能性 但我對哩套戲嘅唔好印象大於好印象<br />\n<br />\n1. 吳彥祖嗰part個人觀感有啲隔硬嚟 甚至覺得有啲多餘 個感覺係導演淨係想用香港啲高樓大廈玩吓災難性層層疊 之後就特登安排佢講個計劃名出嚟咁 有啲唔係好知哩part做乜撚咁<br />\n<br />\n2. 父囡情條線打得唔夠入 感動位覺得有啲尷尬<br />\n<br />\n3. 反角個犯事理由太撚唔合理呱 想炸咗全世界之後做個美國總統 做乜鳩？跟住又係俾人捉到就做5分鐘解說點解佢要犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩屌 娘到一個點<br />\n<br />\n4. 雖然知佢係美國電影 但哩套嘅大美國英雄主義 同埋過份歌頌美國嘅情懷 真係有啲嘔心 尤其最後嗰句咩 「因為老子就是美國總統！」WTF<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係馬後炮 但如果個故事變成美國總統真係背後策劃人 為權力而表面做好人 但暗中搵人阻止男主角 整幾條伏線指向其他角色屈鳩佢哋做反角 而女主角同女船長係總統後後嘅間諜咁 可能會好睇啲<br />\n<br />\nsor 可能太認真 但我真心覺得佢曬咗個idea"},{"pid":"710b6dd0c41780b5c34ec5ca5e1fe74051141185","tid":460322,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/220701_b700f77d380c7446de4c5fe4f48d0a2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F220701_b700f77d380c7446de4c5fe4f48d0a2b.jpg&h=93e43b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/220702_c78d4339f8ac0187511f973a5505986e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F220702_c78d4339f8ac0187511f973a5505986e.jpg&h=fff02515&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得個頭開得唔錯 我嗰時有幾個角色都覺得有做反角嘅可能性 但我對哩套戲嘅唔好印象大於好印象<br />\n<br />\n1. 吳彥祖嗰part個人觀感有啲隔硬嚟 甚至覺得有啲多餘 個感覺係導演淨係想用香港啲高樓大廈玩吓災難性層層疊 之後就特登安排佢講個計劃名出嚟咁 有啲唔係好知哩part做乜撚咁<br />\n<br />\n2. 父囡情條線打得唔夠入 感動位覺得有啲尷尬<br />\n<br />\n3. 反角個犯事理由太撚唔合理呱 想炸咗全世界之後做個美國總統 做乜鳩？跟住又係俾人捉到就做5分鐘解說點解佢要犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩屌 娘到一個點<br />\n<br />\n4. 雖然知佢係美國電影 但哩套嘅大美國英雄主義 同埋過份歌頌美國嘅情懷 真係有啲嘔心 尤其最後